SUMMARY:Poured & Bound: A Boozy Book Club
DESCRIPTION:Sip\, chat\, and dive into great reads with cocktails in hand at Poured & Bound: A Boozy Book Club! \nJoin us for Poured & Bound: A Boozy Book Club!\nPart book club\, part wine night\, part conversation you didn’t know you needed.🍷 \nThis literary tasting invites guests to experience books the way you might sample a flight of wine—through excerpts\, themes\, and guided discussions designed to spark connection and lively debate. Expect playful prompts\, thoughtful conversation\, and a room full of curious\, open-minded people. \nThis month’s theme is Sex\, Desire\, & Becoming 💋 \nCurated Sample Reading List: \n\nHalf His Age by Jeanette McCurdy\nGiovanni’s Room by James Baldwin\nCommunion by Bell Hooks\nMadame Bovary by Gustave Flaubert\n\nDon’t worry\, there’s no homework required. Discussions will be themed around excerpts from the curated reading list. \nPick one\, skim two\, or just come for the conversation. 📚 \nYour ticket includes a wine tasting flight and a curated experience of discussion and connection\, and a 10% discount at Book People for your next read.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/poured-bound-a-boozy-book-club/
LOCATION:Cassette\, 1214 Queen St W\, Toronto\, ON M6J 1J6\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6J 1J6
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink,Literature & Spoken Word,Nightlife
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/poured-bound-a-boozy-book-club.png
END:VEVENT
