SUMMARY:Daniel Romano's Outfit
DESCRIPTION:Toronto music lovers\, welcome to a standout night with Daniel Romano’s Outfit at Main Hall At The Great Hall—one of the city’s favorite rooms for live alternative shows. If you’ve been craving something bold and unpredictable\, this is the kind of local entertainment that hits just right. \nDaniel Romano’s Outfit brings sharp songwriting\, fearless genre-swerves\, and a band dynamic that feels like it could turn on a dime—tight\, loud\, and vividly alive in the moment. Expect surprises\, not a paint-by-numbers set. \nThe Main Hall At The Great Hall offers an intimate\, classic Toronto vibe with great sightlines and a central location that makes getting there easy. It’s the perfect space to feel every note. \nMark Thursday\, December 3\, 2026 at 7:00 PM\, and make it a night—book your spot now for Daniel Romano’s Outfit Toronto.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/daniel-romanos-outfit-2/
LOCATION:The Great Hall\, The Great Hall\, 1087 Queen St. W.\, M6J 1H3 Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada\, Toronto\, M6J 1H3
CATEGORIES:Live Music
