SUMMARY:Questionable - SAPPHIC EDITION : Queer Singles Trivia
DESCRIPTION:Join us at GROUND CONTROL for the event that has become a legend. Always trans and enby inclusive. \nTired of the apps? Is Toronto a tough place to meet new people? Try this! QUESTIONABLE is trivia with a twist…. \nAlready have what you’re looking for but have a friend who you want to set up? Come pitch them! \nThis is our SAPPHIC EDITION. Always trans and enby inclusive. \nCome be part of the series that has become the stuff of legends….. \nThis event is at \nGROUND CONTROL\n1279 Queen Street West \nDoors at 7:30pmFirst Round starts at 8pm\nHosted by your faves:\n@chaodykes\nHow does it work? \nYou will be put in a team with 5-6 people you don’t know. \nThere will be 2 rounds of trivia. Each round\, you will change teams! So\, by the end of the event you will have met 10-12 new people. Each round lasts about 40 minutes – just long enough to get to know someone’s vibe but not so long you are stuck with them all night! \nThere will be a DJ In the lounge after the event so you can stay after the event to keep the conversations going! \nWhat does ‘single’ mean? \n‘Single’ means you are open to connecting with other people for love\, lust or friendship. \nMaybe you will meet your soulmate! Maybe you will meet your new best friend! Maybe you will make out in the bathroom! Maybe you will add a lover to your rotation! Maybe you will find a gaming parter! Basically – you should be available to connect with people in some way. \nThe event is poly-friendly\, slut-friendly\, monogamy-friendly\, ace-friendly. If you can’t leave your judgment of others at home\, then you should stay home. \nSchedule \n7pm – Doors Open\, you get put into your first team \n8pm – First Round starts \n10pm – Expected end\, but you can stay to socialize! \nCost \nWe are doing a sliding scale of $5-$25. \nAll funds are going to Glad Day Lit to support 2SLGBTQ artists and community events. \nHow will you make the teams? \nThe teams will mostly be random. \nHow many people can attend? \nOur max number for this event is 85 people.This event can sell out and the lower price tickets sell out first\, so act fast. \nYou can email any questions to have to: vip@gladday.ca
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/questionable-sapphic-edition-queer-singles-trivia-3/
LOCATION:Ground Control\, 1279 Queen Street West\, Toronto
CATEGORIES:2SLGBTQ+,Games & Trivia
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/questionable-sapphic-edition-queer-singles-trivia.png
END:VEVENT
